== 反響 ==
《金牌拳手》上映後好評如潮<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-et-mn-rocky-creed-production-ryan-coogler-20151123-story.html|title=Getting the 'Rocky' spinoff 'Creed' made was a real underdog story for director Ryan Coogler|website=latimes.com|accessdate=2015-11-25|archive-date=2015-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151124171125/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-et-mn-rocky-creed-production-ryan-coogler-20151123-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據146篇專業評論新鮮度高達92%，平均得分7.9／10；該網站共識：「《金牌拳手》所帶來了《洛基》系列一個令人出乎意料深刻的第七集，儘管堅持走其經典的前身的根本，而在有趣的新方向中延伸了拳擊手的傳奇」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/creed_2015/?search=Creed |title=Creed (2015) |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2015-11-27 |archive-date=2015-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151122075703/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/creed_2015/?search=creed |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分82，代表「普遍好評」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/creed |title=Creed reviews |website=Metacritic |accessdate=2015-11-26 |archive-date=2015-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151128003141/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/creed |dead-url=no }}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾在A+至F之間平均給了「A」的評價<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/11/thanksgiving-box-office-hunger-games-mockingjay-creed-the-good-dinosaur-1201639941/|title=Katniss Rules Wednesday On Track For $78M-80M 5-Day; ‘Good Dinosaur’ Eyes $58M-$62M; ‘Creed’ Punching $39M-$42M|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|work=''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]''|accessdate=2015-11-26|archive-date=2015-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151126233231/http://deadline.com/2015/11/thanksgiving-box-office-hunger-games-mockingjay-creed-the-good-dinosaur-1201639941/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

美國首週以600萬美元的票房登當週第三。

